node.text: I am in the process of searching for my first home and it has been a competitive process, so I sat down with @meredithrealestate to ask questions and get some clarity on how to stay encouraged in this market! Thankful for @bhhscalifornia for their help on this exciting journey!! I used this cover photo to manifest my dream home! #findyourperfect

☺️🎄❤️

node.text: This is the first year in a while that we aren’t on a trip or together on your birthday and I felt so emotional going through all of our photos and videos and all the places we have been! I love you so much and I’m so thankful for your friendship! Can’t wait for our next adventure! ❤️
